# Tor IP Rotator 🌍🛡️

A simple Python tool that routes your traffic through the Tor network and displays geolocated IP addresses. Automatically rotates your Tor identity and shows updated IP info.

---

## 📋 Features

- 🔁 Automatically rotates Tor identity/IP
- 🌐 Shows current IP, City, Country, ISP
- 🧅 Works through Tor SOCKS proxy
- ⚡ Fast, single-threaded execution
- 🐧 Compatible with Kali Linux / Debian systems

---

